---
title: Garlic Herb Butter Steak & Lobster Tails with Lemony Broccoli & Chive Roasted Potatoes
description: No need to make a reservation at a fancy French bistro—bring the white tablecloth vibes to your dinner table with this surf ‘n’ turf dish. Lobster tails are basted with a rich, garlic herb butter, which is also used to top perfectly seared steaks. The duo is paired with lemony roasted broccoli, plus chive-topped roasted potatoes. Bon appétit!
